><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:47:21.000Z","msg":"冇凸個柒頭出黎嚇親人 算係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea09178eb328d636002edd0c436e115294806f79","tid":1300511,"uid":113155,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:50:11.000Z","msg":"咁咪努力做人囉<br />\n老老豆豆 身邊不少而啲人<br />\n但係明明係果啲自怨自憐嘅人<br />\n知自己差 又唔去改 淨係得個灰 得個呻<br />\n樣衰咪執下自己囉 冇文化咪睇多啲書電影畫畫音樂 冇學歷咪進修囉 再不濟咪學好英文或學多種語言囉<br />\n明明係自己冇堅持又淨係識活喺自己comfort zone 覺得自己冇用 而唔去努力改<br />\n你當人人天生靚仔天生醒天生有錢天生有學位<br />\n不排除有 但絕大部分唔係 靚囡都要化妝啦<br />\n不思長進又成日話自己冇用<br />\n事實<br />\n你係冇用 因為你冇堅持去改變你冇用而個事實<br />\n<br />\n成日想屌醒身邊而啲人 但佢哋大多數又心靈脆弱不經屌<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X8JqfZG.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX8JqfZG.gif&h=886178f0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6OEpwx1.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6OEpwx1.gif&h=b5ee40d0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d8FDAZG.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd8FDAZG.gif&h=f8f41f1f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yZUpwx1.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyZUpwx1.gif&h=07f3fbe2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SfbZ4S1.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSfbZ4S1.gif&h=f4c8a570&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9yMOYc2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9yMOYc2.png&h=1cb96e8a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c24648601d1419ba5fa32866635556fbcdab5cc2","tid":1300511,"uid":4787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T12:14:25.000Z","msg":"叫我<br />\n人生最成功既地方就係一直失敗<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a59d3dc4388cc519af34af77ac3d8997e742fdca","tid":